title: Impact If There's No Preseason & Potential of Spring College Football
itunes:title: Impact If There's No Preseason & Potential of Spring College Football
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys discuss the impact if there's no preseason games from a variety of viewpoints (:47). Next, the duo look at the potential of spring college football and the different scenarios that could happen (22:30). After that, the pair react to the news of no supplemental draft in 2020 (28:52). To wrap up the show, DJ and Bucky talk more about the possible scenario of Power 5 conferences also playing college football in the spring (32:22).
